entries.content: A negative reply or 'no' is valuable data.
entries.notes: Helps disqualify or remove prospects from sequences/campaigns.

entries.content: 'Not interested' objections, especially in emails, often stem from the salesperson talking about themselves instead of the prospect.
entries.notes: Focus on the prospect to avoid causing objections.

focus_area: Objection Discovery: Clarifying questions, isolation, root cause
